{"tha-ap563:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap563:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap563:0.3":"Ratthapalattheraapadana ","tha-ap563:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap563:1.2":"Lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap563:1.3":"Varanago maya dinno, ","tha-ap563:1.4":"Isadanto urulhava. ","tha-ap563:2.1":"Setacchattopasobhito, ","tha-ap563:2.2":"sakappano sahatthipo; ","tha-ap563:2.3":"Agghapetvana tam sabbam, ","tha-ap563:2.4":"sangharamam akarayim. ","tha-ap563:3.1":"Catupannasasahassani, ","tha-ap563:3.2":"pasade karayim aham; ","tha-ap563:3.3":"Mahoghadanam karitvana, ","tha-ap563:3.4":"niyyadesim mahesino. ","tha-ap563:4.1":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap563:4.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap563:4.3":"Sabbe jane hasayanto, ","tha-ap563:4.4":"desesi amatam padam. ","tha-ap563:5.1":"Tam me buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap563:5.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap563:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap563:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap563:6.1":"‘Catupannasasahassani, ","tha-ap563:6.2":"pasade karayi ayam; ","tha-ap563:6.3":"Kathayissami vipakam, ","tha-ap563:6.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap563:7.1":"Attharasasahassani, ","tha-ap563:7.2":"kutagara bhavissare; ","tha-ap563:7.3":"Byamhuttamamhi nibbatta, ","tha-ap563:7.4":"sabbasonnamaya ca te. ","tha-ap563:8.1":"Pannasakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap563:8.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap563:8.3":"Atthapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap563:8.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap563:9.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap563:9.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap563:9.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap563:9.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap563:10.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap563:10.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap563:10.3":"Addhe kule mahabhoge, ","tha-ap563:10.4":"nibbattissati tavade. ","tha-ap563:11.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap563:11.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap563:11.3":"Ratthapaloti namena, ","tha-ap563:11.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap563:12.1":"Padhanapahitatto so, ","tha-ap563:12.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap563:12.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap563:12.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap563:13.1":"Utthaya abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap563:13.2":"jahita bhogasampada; ","tha-ap563:13.3":"Khelapindeva bhogamhi, ","tha-ap563:13.4":"pemam mayham na vijjati. ","tha-ap563:14.1":"Viriyam me dhuradhorayham, ","tha-ap563:14.2":"yogakkhemadhivahanam; ","tha-ap563:14.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap563:14.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap563:15.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap563:15.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap563:15.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap563:16.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap563:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap563:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap563:17.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap563:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap563:17.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap563:18.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ratthapalo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap563:19.1":"Ratthapalattherassapadanam ekadasamam. ","tha-ap563:20.1":"Yasavaggo chapannasamo. ","tha-ap563:21.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap563:22.1":"Yaso nadikassapo ca, ","tha-ap563:22.2":"gayakimilavajjino; ","tha-ap563:22.3":"Duve uttara bhaddaji, ","tha-ap563:22.4":"sivako upavahano; ","tha-ap563:22.5":"Ratthapalo ekasatam, ","tha-ap563:22.6":"gathanam pancanavuti. ","tha-ap563:23.1":"Therapadanam samattam. "}